  <name>Digital: A Love Story</name>
  <summary>A computer mystery/romance set five minutes into the future of 1988</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A computer mystery/romance set five minutes into the future of 1988.
    </p>
    <p>
      I can guarantee at least ONE of the following is a real feature:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Discover a vast conspiracy lurking on the internet!</li>
      <li>Save the world by exploiting a buffer overflow!</li>
      <li>Get away with telephone fraud!</li>
      <li>HACK THE GIBSON!</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Which one? You'll have to dial in and see. Welcome to the 20th century.
    </p>
    <p>
      A pre-NaNoRenO release. Digital is released under a Creative Commons license. February 2010, by Christine Love.
    </p>
  </description>

